OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,FThe founder of parkrun has said that a
OL,8,Fmillion events was "never in the plan"
OL,9,Fas the charity is set to reach the
OL,10,Fmilestone this weekend.
OL,12,FThere were just 13 runners and five
OL,13,Fvolunteers when Paul Sinton-Hewitt
OL,14,Forganised the first parkrun ` then
OL,15,Fcalled Bushy Park Time Trial ` at
OL,16,FBushy Park in London in October 2004.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
