FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,FIt has evolved into a global community
OL,8,Fof free, weekly, timed 5km parkruns on
OL,9,FSaturdays, and 2km junior parkruns on
OL,10,FSundays, with more than 2,800 event
OL,11,Flocations in 23 countries.
OL,13,F"To have done a million events, there
OL,14,Fisn't a single event organisation in
OL,15,Fthe world apart from parkrun who might
OL,16,Fbe even close to that," said Mr Sinton-
OL,17,FHewitt, 65.
OL,19,F"Nobody ever thought we would get to a
OL,20,Fmillion.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@WO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,F"It was never in the plan.
OL,9,F"But of course now the next million's
OL,10,Fgoing to come so much quicker.
OL,12,F"It's not going to be 20 years, that's
OL,13,Ffor sure."
OL,15,FHe said the "numbers are
OL,16,Fextraordinary" and added: "There are
OL,17,Fmany people who've been born since we
OL,18,Fstarted parkrun who just don't
OL,19,Funderstand a world where parkrun
OL,20,Fdoesn't exist.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUuD@JO]wD@MOUxD@NO]xD@
OL,26,A[OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,F"It's like knowing that you have
OL,8,Fbreakfast every morning.
OL,10,F"It's so part of their lives."
OL,12,FHe said he does not get involved in
OL,13,Fthe day-to-day running of parkrun and
OL,14,Fis "hoping in a year or so's time to
OL,15,Fretire from the organisation".
OL,17,F"I think the positive message from
OL,18,Fthat is I think that we have such a
OL,19,Fgreat team right now that I'm in a
OL,20,Fposition to consider retirement," said
OL,21,FMr Sinton-Hewitt.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUrD@^O]vD@DOUwD@]O]yD@AOU|D@
OL,26,AaO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,F"The only involvement I should have is
OL,8,Fwhere the team wants me to be
OL,9,Finvolved, and I think that the future
OL,10,Fof parkrun is safe and secure."
OL,12,FIn January, the King attended
OL,13,FSandringham parkrun in Norfolk as a
OL,14,Fspectator.
OL,16,FMr Sinton-Hewitt, who now lives near
OL,17,FHorsham, Sussex, said: "I'd love to
OL,18,Fmeet the King, I'd love to have them
OL,19,Finvolved on a more regular basis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@_O]yD@XOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
