OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,F"But the fact he chose to go down to
OL,8,FSandringham parkrun and to cheer
OL,9,Feverybody on, that is a huge accolade
OL,10,Ffor parkrun and we're very, very proud
OL,11,Fof that."
OL,13,FHe said the success of parkrun was
OL,14,F"clearly down to the simplicity... the
OL,15,Ffact it is for everybody, inclusivity,
OL,16,Fthe nature of that, the fact that it's
OL,17,Ffree".
OL,19,F"For somebody who's coming to running
OL,20,Ffor the first time... a barrier gets
OL,21,Ftaken away," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]vD@AOUyD@EO]{D@AOU}D@LO]
