PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,FThe first parkrunner to participate in
OL,8,F1,000 parkruns, Darren Wood, reached
OL,9,Fthe milestone last month.
OL,11,FMr Sinton-Hewitt, who has completed
OL,12,F614 parkruns, said that 1,000 parkruns
OL,13,F"feels a million miles away" but
OL,14,F"maybe when I turn 80 I'll get it".
OL,16,FHe said parkrun is introducing new
OL,17,Fmilestone T-shirts for every 100
OL,18,Fparkruns.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@\O]vD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
