PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,F"The one thing that we do at parkrun
OL,8,Fis we try to celebrate everything,
OL,9,Fregardless of your PB," he said.
OL,11,F"The fact we've introduced these
OL,12,Fmilestones at every 100, it makes
OL,13,Fsense.
OL,15,F"If you think back to the beginning we
OL,16,Fdidn't have any money and it was
OL,17,Freally difficult to provide the
OL,18,Fmilestone T-shirts so we just went
OL,19,F250, 500, thinking nobody would get
OL,20,Fthere, but of course we've been proven
OL,21,Fwrong."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@WO]sD@AOUwD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
