CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,FHe said he is "not running much any
OL,8,Fmore because (the) knees just can't do
OL,9,Fit" but he still tries to "do the odd
OL,10,Fwalk and quite a lot of volunteering".
OL,12,F"The one thing that's still consistent
OL,13,Fis I still love parkrun and I still
OL,14,Flove being there," he said.
OL,16,FElizabeth Duggan, chief executive
OL,17,Fofficer of parkrun Global, said that
OL,18,Fhitting one million events this
OL,19,Fweekend is "just phenomenal".
OL,26,@oD@OOUqD@CO]qD@[OUrD@eO]tD@AOUvD@RO]{D@
OL,26,ALOU{D@\O]
