OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,FShe said parkrun has "massive
OL,8,Fambitions for the future", including
OL,9,Fto increase the number of parkrun
OL,10,Fcountries from 23 to 30 by 2030.
OL,12,F"We have about half a million
OL,13,Fparticipants every single weekend
OL,14,Fglobally and we believe by 2030 we
OL,15,Fwill be hitting three quarters of a
OL,16,Fmillion," she said.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@YO]tD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
