OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781529076
OL,3,CA million events was never in the
OL,4,Cplan, says parkrun founder as
OL,5,Cmilestone nears
OL,7,FShe said that parkrun is launching its
OL,8,Ffirst health and inclusion strategy in
OL,9,Fthe UK, adding: "We know that we want
OL,10,Fto reach more people globally, but we
OL,11,Falso know that we need to reach more
OL,12,Fand different people."
OL,14,FShe stressed that parkrun is a charity
OL,15,Fand "can only exist if people continue
OL,16,Fto support us".
OL,26,@qD@QOUtD@VO]wD@EOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
